I know what you're thinking, why do you continue to buy them right? I suppose I'm just stubborn and want them so badly that I continue to tell myself hopefully they'll be good this time. I cannot get my money back because I refuse to pay for delivery service yet have to go into the store EVERY SINGLE TIME I get a delivery to return the item. Makes delivery pointless. * And yes you're seeing this right, aside from the fur (mold), that IS a WORM inside the berry in the last pic!!! so much money down the drain.
